Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H2D27A3&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke, who was killed by the \Ngreat organization GOD along with his father...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...revived as Kamen Rider X, thanks to his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Keisuke's lover, Ryouko, side with GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is Kiriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who fights against the mysterious GOD, Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Japanese Islands Fragmentation Plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Be careful! There's ammunition inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna explode! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bus incident in Onigamizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All the passengers including the driver were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Police are investigating, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the ammunition in the underground room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's GOD General Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullman Minotaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you've successfully carried the ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll cause a civil war in Japan with these weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Won't you tell me why you were there all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a father and mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They both died in the bus accident that happened the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother! Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She lost her parents in that accident, and now she's alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be responsible for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachiko, this man is a great person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll take good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachiko, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a lot of friends who are just about your age. {Tachibana.......}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be able to get along with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And you won't be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This man right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost his father too, and yet he's still bright and happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not lonely now, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, that incident seems really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They say the bus fell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe G.O.D is behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to find some evidence, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look after the girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I am one of G.O.D's cyborgs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oxman Minotaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was Ryouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Come back as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The child is heading for the graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being taken care of by an old man, and a kind young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still lonely, but I'll do my best to live life fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go to heaven without worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just attacked by G.O.D, near where that accident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was them after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But he ran away, so I don't know where their base is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is the girl okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she was putting flowers on her parents' grave, but she hasn't returned yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain she did come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Sachiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I heard a girl's scream coming from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my ears are special. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a ribbon that I bought for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you've fallen into my trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, and the girl will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You would even threaten children?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tie them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it, Jin Keisuke
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you can't turn into Rider X anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exacting my revenge, as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, put them on the truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Load these weapons onto the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I need these weapons for my grand plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wars will be started throughout Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But your lives will end before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,G.O.D, why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we'll set this place to explode soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Set up the bomb's timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll explode in three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,May you happily move on to the next world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I don't care what you do to me, just let the other two live!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! At least let the little girl live, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To expect sympathy from G.O.D, you really are naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The next world will be much happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it fell off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But am I really going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Can't we do something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to save the girl, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't do anything with our hands bound like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray. Pray to the God of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kiriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For rescuing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, hurry and pursue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That is your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Great Spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, you're still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as GOD exists, I won't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan to bring weapons into Japan, and turn it into a battlefield, were thwarted by X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However, what's the next target?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.09,0:23:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, fight! Kamen Rider X of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.16,0:23:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.37,0:23:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"The Terrifying Human Genius Plan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.15,0:23:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.15,0:23:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
